{
  "stem": "5248.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I-- I-- I-- I-- I knew that it existed, but it never came very close to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The maids in our house or many people that my father employed were non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to travel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some experiences-- well, we used to go to swim to a lake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that apparently was site of anti-Semitism, because you had to compete with-- with those, let's say, country boys, or older boys, who are good swimmer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I learned to swim quite early.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they never touch me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we did hear a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hear about Crystal-- Crystal Night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hear about actually Jewish people who had Polish citizenship were expelled from Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- and we had some of those people, but although they told us certain things, we did not believe, or were very skeptical about.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we got some families which came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kids joined the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they taught us about, but we thought that we are protected, especially when the war became-- starts readying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We felt that Chamberlain will-- will do everything for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A matter of fact, I write this-- I wrote a short story how-- how-- how much kids and adults were mistaken or had delusion that nothing will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although on this time, there was a new party in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pilsudki died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was Marshal Pilsudski.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He died in '36.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the new government, the man who took over was not-- he was a rather tolerant man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the new man was not that tolerant, so-- although he not had that much prestige or power.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was a new party-- a-- national party to the-- to the right, which start spreading anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
